{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_05_01_short",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 ついに女優デビュー！ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "成宮すず！　{user}さんの\n呼び出しに応じて、来てあげましたわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu Narumiya! I've come\nin response to your call‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……相変わらず元気だな\n忙しい中、来てもらってすまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Still full of energy‚ huh?\nYou're busy‚ yet you came. Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "他ならぬ{user}さんの呼び出しですもの\nそれに、打ち合わせも仕事のうちです。お気になさらず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's your call‚ {user}-san‚ not just anyone else's.\nAnd besides‚ meetings are a part of work. Don't worry about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、私に直接話したいことってなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But more importantly‚ what kind of talk\ndid you want to have with me directly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4149431069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、仕事の話なんだけど……今までと違うタイプの\n仕事だから、直接説明した方がいいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's about our schedule… It's something different from\nwhat we've done so far‚ so I thought I'd discuss it with you directly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "今までと違うお仕事、ですって？\n……ふっ、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something different from what we've done so far?\n…Heh‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私はもう駆け出しの新人アイドルでは\nありませんわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not just a rookie idol\nwho debuted not too long ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9419503212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロを背負って立つ『二代目星降る奇跡』\nこの成宮すずに、そんな気遣いは無用ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bear the title of \"Second Generation Starry Miracle\"\nfrom Hoshimi Production.\nYou don't need to worry about such things with me‚\nSuzu Narumiya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "どんな仕事でも余裕でこなしてご覧に入れます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what it is‚ I can handle it easily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、なら良かった。あのな、実は……\nすずに連続テレビドラマの出演オファーがきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ then I can rest easy. Actually…\nI received an offer for you to appear in a TV drama.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.6,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}